response.overview: In 1987, during the austere days of Thatcher’s Britain, a teenager learns to live life, understand his family, and find his own voice through the music of Bruce Springsteen.
response.tagline: For anyone who has ever wanted to dream. You're not alone.
response.title: Blinded by the Light
